About
The Grand Garden Arena at MGM Grand Las Vegas has played host to hundreds of events in its 30 years of existence, from spectacular concerts, championship fights, premier sports action and special events.

Setting aside the abysmal exiting policy that slows down everyone attempting to leave after a show The MGM Grand Garden Arena remains an iconic venue that gets it right in terms of sound. As the smallest arena on Pearl Jam's 2024 Dark Matter Tour prices were typical for Las Vegas but the guys put on two stellar nights of music including 26 songs on Thursday the 16th and 25 more on Saturday the 18th. Everything sounded great and visuals were also on point. Far better than T-mobile in terms of acoustics, though flow and merchandise could use some work.
